name: Spicy Like Good Eggnog (I Like Eggnog)

sections.name: Working to Get Ready to Work

exercise.name: Jog in Place
exercise.description: Start in a standing position with your feet underneath your hips.. Be quick off the ground,, as you alternate your legs up and down to jog in place.

exercise.name: Spiderman Stretch
exercise.description: Start in a high plank and lunge your right leg forward keeping both hands to the left of your right leg. Keeping your right leg at ninety degrees, hold, bring your foot back and repeat on the other side

audios.text: Start in a high plank and lunge your right leg forward keeping both hands to the left of your right leg. Keeping your right leg at ninety degrees, hold, bring your foot back and repeat on the other side

exercise.name: Prayer Stretch
exercise.description: Starting in a childs pose sitting back on your heels, reach your right arm and press the palm into the floor.  Left hand behind your head, rotate left, stretching your back and chest.
exercise.synonyms: Quadruped Tspine Rotation,T Spine Rotation,T-Spine Rotation

audios.text: Starting in a childs pose sitting back on your heels, reach your right arm and press the palm into the floor.  Left hand behind your head, rotate left, stretching your back and chest.

exercise.name: Prayer Stretch
exercise.description: Starting in a childs pose sitting back on your heels, reach your left arm and press the palm into the floor.  Right hand behind your head, rotate right, stretching your back and chest.
exercise.synonyms: Quadruped Tspine Rotation,T Spine Rotation,T-Spine Rotation

audios.text: Starting in a childs pose sitting back on your heels, reach your left arm and press the palm into the floor.  Right hand behind your head, rotate right, stretching your back and chest.

exercise.name: Cat Camel
exercise.description: Start with your hands and knees on the ground.. Exhale as you reach the bottom of your sternum towards the ceiling.. To reverse, inhale as you arch your low back,, and finish by looking up..

exercise.name: Inchworms
exercise.description: Fold over and place your hands on the ground.  Taking small steps with your hands, walk out into a plank position.  While keeping your legs straight, walk your feet up to your hands.

audios.text: Fold over and place your hands on the ground.  Taking small steps with your hands, walk out into a plank position.  While keeping your legs straight, walk your feet up to your hands.

exercise.name: Reverse Lunge Reaches
exercise.description: Step back and drop down with your knee hovering just above the ground.  On the side that stepped back, reach your arm up to the ceiling.

audios.text: Step back and drop down with your knee hovering just above the ground.  On the side that stepped back, reach your arm up to the ceiling

exercise.name: Barbell Row
exercise.description: Start with the bar just below your knees and your back flat.. Maintain that position as you drive your elbows backwards to squeeze the bar into your chest.. Lower the bar under control and repeat..

exercise.name: Dumbbell Pullover
exercise.description: Bridge up and hold.. Keep your arms straight with your ribs down,, and core engaged.. Allow the dumbbell to move slowly overhead,, and return it just above your chest..

exercise.name: Kneeling Quadriceps Stretch
exercise.description: Kneel on the floor with your right leg forward and left leg back.  With perfect posture, press your hips forward until your feel a stretch in the front of your left thigh.

audios.text: Kneel on the floor with your right leg forward and left leg back.  With perfect posture, press your hips forward until your feel a stretch in the front of your left thigh.
Kneel on the floor with your right leg forward and left leg back.  With perfect posture, press your hips forward until your feel a stretch in the front of your left thigh.

exercise.name: Kneeling Quadriceps Stretch
exercise.description: Kneel on the floor with your left leg forward and right leg back.  With perfect posture, press your hips forward until your feel a stretch in the front of your right thigh.

audios.text: Kneel on the floor with your left leg forward and right leg back.  With perfect posture, press your hips forward until your feel a stretch in the front of your right thigh.

audio_timings.text: now switch to your right leg

exercise.name: Lower Back Stretch
exercise.description: Hug your left knee up towards your chest and pull it across your body with your right hand.  As you breathe out let your left arm drape on the floor as your work deeper into the stretch

audios.text: Hug your left knee up towards your chest and pull it across your body with your right hand.  As you breathe out let your left arm drape on the floor as your work deeper into the stretch

exercise.name: Lower Back Stretch
exercise.description: Hug your right knee up towards your chest and pull it across your body with your right hand.  As you breathe out let your right arm drape on the floor.

audios.text: Hug your right knee up towards your chest and pull it across your body with your right hand.  As you breathe out let your right arm drape on the floor.

exercise.name: Crossbody Lat Stretch
exercise.description: In a child's pose sitting back on your heels, reach your left arm across your body and place the back of your palm on the floor.  Lock that hand down with your right hand, sit back and feel the stretch down your left side.

audios.text: In a child's pose sitting back on your heels, reach your left arm across your body and place the back of your palm on the floor.  Lock that hand down with your right hand, sit back and feel the stretch down your left side.
